name: Verify Underwriter Manager should be displayed next to Underwriter Name for Renewals Reports

testSteps.description: 1: Verify Underwriter Manager should be displayed next to Underwriter Name for Renewals Reports ({Reports=Upcoming Renewals})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And select Reports 'Upcoming Renewals' from Renewals
When user select Underwriting Overview 'Underwriting Overview' from VIEW
Then the field 'UNDERWRITER MANAGER' should be displayed next to 'UNDERWRITER NAME'

testSteps.description: 2: Verify Underwriter Manager should be displayed next to Underwriter Name for Renewals Reports ({Reports=Renewals In Progress})

testSteps.description: 3: Verify Underwriter Manager should be displayed next to Underwriter Name for Renewals Reports ({Reports=Non Renewals})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
